HEADWORD: Alogian
<hw>A*lo"gi*an</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>Alogiani</ets>, <ets>Alogii</ets>, fr. Gr. <?/; <grk>'a</grk> priv.
